{"tid":27873,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次出國去旅行,有咩要注意?","createTime":"2016-12-07T15:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T09:32:08.000Z","uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6406237de73892369d75681dea7fbae4d920624d","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲大家好,小弟第一次出國旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a96efe061e9553f320e19c30128efc7b520c1c","tid":27873,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位巴絲大家好,小弟第一次出國旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小心屁屁"},{"pid":"75319f9c2fa911f4ef3837421158dafba662c822","tid":27873,"uid":45192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"記得帶passport"},{"pid":"f2493da1b8c37fed1eb3edf8776d9c42f955abab","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"唔小心HI中,自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次旅行,去沙巴有咩要注意?<br />\n仲有問題想問下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.1我搭Air.asia,用mobile check in係咪就咁帶passport去機場就得?<br />\n去到比個code佢掃就得?<br />\nQ.2我係晚機去早機返,咁去到係凌晨,應該BOOK埋個2晚定訓機場好?<br />\n還是求其搵一間訓左去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.3我搵過三星酒店(住3晚),但唔知邊間好,想大家推介下(主要安全問題-我自己一個去)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.4想大家介紹下有咩地方好去/必去,我淨係知個加雅肉骨荼,其他都係麵之類<br />\nQ.5上網睇話4季如夏,係咪真?咁我帶短褲都可以??<br />\n<br />\n我知我咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我網上搵好多都係年幾年前既野<br />\n我又未出過省城,所以求各位指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a2b7a4acc0e0ddfa8d2b57c5edfc8b8cda898c","tid":27873,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"你自己唔想咁辛苦咪book酒店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怕辛苦想慳錢咪訓機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁都好問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78c1b928f2988f874f20c3e302800fd7bcf0d23","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己唔想咁辛苦咪book酒店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怕辛苦想慳錢咪訓機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都好問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己一個去,怕安全問題,人生路不熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知我咁大個仔咩都唔識係好弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea08b30cde32daaa05576533a3eb83020e91fc5","tid":27873,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"你唔好問住先啦"},{"pid":"e6adc8f3aaf223c2b6e0f75eeaca778824ed94b5","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔好問住先啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇去過沙巴既巴絲可以施予援助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8d3da21e247d692a1b6120d71ed582cbe1209e","tid":27873,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"冇搭過Air Asia，冇去過沙巴，不過應該都答到你大部分問題<br />\n<br />\n手機check in應該冇托運行李先得，如果有你一樣要去櫃臺<br />\n<br />\n瞓唔瞓機場呢，你就google下你個機場喺邊叫咩名，搵下有冇人瞓過同咩評價，相信你睇完自己都會知瞓唔瞓好；唔想咁攰嘅，咪豪少少瞓晚機場酒店 (如有)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://酒店評價可以睇下booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9D%87%E4%B8%8Bbooking.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=514ed35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">酒店評價可以睇下booking.com</a> agoda <a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e055b15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotel.com</a> tripadvisor呢種，再唔係睇到啱心水嘅google下，睇下住過嘅人點講<br />\n<br />\n天氣呢，都係google下，或者求其搵weather app/當地天文台，搵下你去嗰日咩氣溫，我自己25度打上就一定短褲<br />\n<br />\n大個仔啦，自己善用下Google先，ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd94a8dbe71a567d529ba6d0f1804847243a7a69","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇搭過Air Asia，冇去過沙巴，不過應該都答到你大部分問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機check in應該冇托運行李先得，如果有你一樣要去櫃臺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瞓唔瞓機場呢，你就google下你個機場喺邊叫咩名，搵下有冇人瞓過同咩評價，相信你睇完自己都會知瞓唔瞓好；唔想咁攰嘅，咪豪少少瞓晚機場酒店 (如有)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://酒店評價可以睇下booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E8%A9%95%E5%83%B9%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9D%87%E4%B8%8Bbooking.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=514ed35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">酒店評價可以睇下booking.com</a> agoda <a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e055b15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotel.com</a> tripadvisor呢種，再唔係睇到啱心水嘅google下，睇下住過嘅人點講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天氣呢，都係google下，或者求其搵weather app/當地天文台，搵下你去嗰日咩氣溫，我自己25度打上就一定短褲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大個仔啦，自己善用下Google先，ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係Google嘛<br />\n主要我想問酒店 網上寫好平 有$500hkd以下<br />\n我想知係咪實價(唔包10%服務費) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f953279e442f2bb0839d873697dee4f3dc4f0a","tid":27873,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇搭過Air Asia，冇去過沙巴，不過應該都答到你大部分問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機check in應該冇托運行李先得，如果有你一樣要去櫃臺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瞓唔瞓機場呢，你就google下你個機場喺邊叫咩名，搵下有冇人瞓過同咩評價，相信你睇完自己都會知瞓唔瞓好；唔想咁攰嘅，咪豪少少瞓晚機場酒店 (如有)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n酒店評價可以睇下<a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=992908ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://booking.com</a> agoda <a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=e055b15e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hotel.com</a> tripadvisor呢種，再唔係睇到啱心水嘅google下，睇下住過嘅人點講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天氣呢，都係google下，或者求其搵weather app/當地天文台，搵下你去嗰日咩氣溫，我自己25度打上就一定短褲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大個仔啦，自己善用下Google先，ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係Google嘛<br />\n主要我想問酒店 網上寫好平 有$500hkd以下<br />\n我想知係咪實價(唔包10%服務費) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撳入去會寫明<br />\n再唔係臨比錢嗰下都會寫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://印象中booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8D%B0%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%ADbooking.com&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7d48747a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">印象中booking.com</a>個價唔包稅同服務費<br />\n其他網多數會包"},{"pid":"acb2ac403cf62a95f6053a969fb3276e6ed98f16","tid":27873,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係Google嘛<br />\n主要我想問酒店 網上寫好平 有$500hkd以下<br />\n我想知係咪實價(唔包10%服務費) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook酒店你懶既話去trivago同埋hotelscombined打個日子就睇得哂個價錢，呢兩個係格價網<br />\n<br />\n睇酒店好唔好我多數會用TripAdvisor，排名高既多數冇伏"},{"pid":"28a58353576b9f45f330f5ace40e498b3cace51f","tid":27873,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔小心HI中,自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次旅行,去沙巴有咩要注意?<br />\n仲有問題想問下各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.1我搭Air.asia,用mobile check in係咪就咁帶passport去機場就得?<br />\n去到比個code佢掃就得?<br />\nQ.2我係晚機去早機返,咁去到係凌晨,應該BOOK埋個2晚定訓機場好?<br />\n還是求其搵一間訓左去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.3我搵過三星酒店(住3晚),但唔知邊間好,想大家推介下(主要安全問題-我自己一個去)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nQ.4想大家介紹下有咩地方好去/必去,我淨係知個加雅肉骨荼,其他都係麵之類<br />\nQ.5上網睇話4季如夏,係咪真?咁我帶短褲都可以??<br />\n<br />\n我知我咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我網上搵好多都係年幾年前既野<br />\n我又未出過省城,所以求各位指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1. 其實就算你有冇web check in 都好，帶passport已經好夠，地勤有你passport個人資料已經可以幫你check in同寄行李，不過web check in左就有boarding pass你冇行李可以直接入禁區上機<br />\n<br />\n當然都有人有兩手準備，print左張eticket出黎或者print個boarding pass出黎<br />\n<br />\n2. 我就未試過係沙巴機場訓教，但個機場都幾新，但馬拉乜人都有，如果唔係窮到仆街我建議你book多一兩日平少少既酒店訓<br />\n<br />\n3. 你住乜酒店都好，貴重野跟身，冇話邊間特別安全<br />\n<br />\n4. 沙巴好多野玩，自己上網search下<br />\n<br />\n5. 馬拉全年都咁熱係常識黎"},{"pid":"af35f6e619f7c624e3de6cbb4f42f9f3e551e4eb","tid":27873,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:28:08.000Z","msg":"去過馬拉好多次<br />\n<br />\n提多你一樣野，錢可以係機場銀聯機撳，個rate唔錯(上網check到)，未必係最平，但方便快捷<br />\n<br />\n另外沙巴有個商場叫Wisma Merdeka入面d鋪個rate都ok(好似係)"},{"pid":"73a135f2b1ebcc21a7f2a86bbd497e6a08c1f568","tid":27873,"uid":44702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過馬拉好多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提多你一樣野，錢可以係機場銀聯機撳，個rate唔錯(上網check到)，未必係最平，但方便快捷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外沙巴有個商場叫Wisma Merdeka入面d鋪個rate都ok(好似係)</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經搵左,會到時先cheak in<br />\n.如果買機票無買揀位坐,上到去冇人坐既位可以調?<br />\n.想知有冇咩地方特別要去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759e7fe54651789505cc0d0598c2a4288d3dea4c","tid":27873,"uid":41461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"你機場托運行李嗰陣 工作人員會print張broading pass比你 上面有你坐個位<br />\n你當時可以要求換位(成功機會唔大)  例如窗口走廊位之類。<br />\n唔係上到機自己見邊度有空位就坐邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}